<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-07-17T23:59:59-04:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-01-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="148" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d148">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                        </head>
                        <p>The ceremony on the occasion of the signing of the North Atlantic Treaty
                            included remarks by the twelve participating Foreign Ministers and an
                            address by President Truman. For texts of these statements, see
                            Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, April 17, 1949,
                            page 471.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>